                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "8ZPzF",
                      "name": "bio1",
                      "fill": "$muted-fg",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "I'm Dario Djuric, and I'm a software engineer born and living in Zagreb, Croatia. I love to write, and this blog is a place where I love to share all the things I learn.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.625,
                      "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "WQGNz",
                      "name": "bio2",
                      "fill": "$muted-fg",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "I have over 15 years of experience working in different areas of IT. After finishing college, I started to work as a network engineer, then shortly worked as an SAP consultant, after which I returned to my passion from my high school days, which is software development.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.625,
                      "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "T9ptY",
                      "name": "bio3",
                      "fill": "$muted-fg",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Since then, I've worked mostly in the service/consulting space in the enterprise, and I've led teams, small and large. Currently, I work as a freelancer, specializing in JavaScript and TypeScript on both the frontend and the backend.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.625,
                      "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "s3xOH",
                      "name": "bio4",
                      "fill": "$muted-fg",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Outside of work, most of my time is spent with my wife and our two boys, and every once in a while I manage to squeeze in a bit of time for my hobbies: sports, guitar playing, or being a home barista (a title that justifies me spending a lot on my coffee gear).",
                      "lineHeight": 1.625,
                      "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
